videos.headline: Georgia Tech defense strip sacks Daniel Jones
videos.description: Georgia Tech's defense comes up big as Tre Swilling strip sacks Duke's  Daniel Jones.

videos.headline: Georgia Tech's Marshall finds Carter for 68-yard TD
videos.description: Georgia Tech gets on the board as TaQuon Marshall finds a wide open Malachi Carter  for a 68-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Duke and Georgia Tech altercation leads to ejection
videos.description: A fight breaks out between  Duke and Georgia Tech following a kickoff return, Georgia Tech's Victor Alexander is ejected for throwing punches.

videos.headline: Duke's Jones airs it out to find Rahming for a 48-yard TD
videos.description: Daniel Jones finds a wide open T.J. Rahming for a 48-yard  Duke touchdown.

videos.headline: Duke's Jones throws a dart to Koppenhaver for 1-yard TD
videos.description: Daniel Jones leads Duke down the field again as he throws to Davis Koppenhaver for a 1-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Duke's Jones throws his 3rd TD of the day
videos.description: Daniel Jones continues to dominate as he finds Johnathan Lloyd for a 6-yard Duke touchdown.
